00:33:56,210 --> 00:33:57,460
Tomorrow, I'll take you all...

585
00:33:57,460 --> 00:33:57,980
We've lost her.

586
00:33:57,980 --> 00:33:58,940
To a new journey.

587
00:33:58,940 --> 00:33:59,620
Come with me.

588
00:34:03,500 --> 00:34:04,740
She's indeed a police officer.

589
00:34:05,540 --> 00:34:07,060
She's very meticulous.

590
00:34:08,580 --> 00:34:09,699
Come on, tourists.

591
00:34:09,699 --> 00:34:10,929
Follow me closely.

592
00:34:10,929 --> 00:34:11,860
Don't get separated.

593
00:34:12,540 --> 00:34:14,980
The room has been arranged for you.

594
00:34:16,860 --> 00:34:17,900
Let's take out our IDs.

595
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:20,100
Line up here and register.

596
00:34:21,260 --> 00:34:22,780
I'll distribute the room cards to you.

597
00:34:29,620 --> 00:34:30,739
Here, this is yours.

598
00:34:30,940 --> 00:34:31,730
Thank you.

599
00:34:32,219 --> 00:34:34,580
You can leave your big suitcases

600
00:34:34,580 --> 00:34:36,739
to the porter.

601
00:34:36,860 --> 00:34:38,420
He will then send them

602
00:34:38,420 --> 00:34:40,620
to every one of your room later.

603
00:34:40,860 --> 00:34:41,420
Don't worry.

604
00:34:41,420 --> 00:34:43,100
This is a service for free.

605
00:34:43,980 --> 00:34:45,179
Here, this is yours.

606
00:34:49,659 --> 00:34:51,980
You must keep a close eye on our guests' belongings.

607
00:34:53,219 --> 00:34:53,900
Okay.

608
00:34:56,219 --> 00:34:57,300
Guys at the back.

609
00:34:57,300 --> 00:34:58,100
Move forward.

610
00:34:59,620 --> 00:35:00,980
Here's your room card.

611
00:35:00,980 --> 00:35:02,210
Let's go and eat first.

612
00:35:02,380 --> 00:35:04,930
We'll go back to our room after the meal.

613
00:36:03,570 --> 00:36:04,060
Jin.

614
00:36:04,060 --> 00:36:05,060
We have news.

615
00:36:05,060 --> 00:36:06,860
We found the truck at an abandoned repair factory in the suburbs.

616
00:36:06,860 --> 00:36:07,740
Copy that.

617
00:36:09,220 --> 00:36:10,700
We have news. I'll take you there.

618
00:36:58,180 --> 00:36:59,100
Do you need help?

619
00:36:59,300 --> 00:37:01,220
It's okay. I can deal with it myself.

620
00:37:01,900 --> 00:37:02,540
Are you sure?

621
00:37:03,620 --> 00:37:04,340
Don't worry.

622
00:37:04,340 --> 00:37:05,300
Thanks, Jin.

623
00:37:06,310 --> 00:37:11,430
[Taxi]

624
00:37:34,540 --> 00:37:36,180
I know I'm not good at guns.

625
00:37:36,900 --> 00:37:38,130
I have a card up my sleeve.

626
00:37:39,020 --> 00:37:40,700
This gift was prepared for Da Hui.

627
00:37:41,820 --> 00:37:43,540
I didn't expect to give it to you.

628
00:38:03,460 --> 00:38:04,340
I'll cover you!

629
00:39:11,780 --> 00:39:12,540
Calm down.

630
00:39:14,020 --> 00:39:15,020
Shoot!

631
00:39:15,780 --> 00:39:16,340
Come on!

632
00:39:16,340 --> 00:39:17,820
Don't kill me!

633
00:39:17,820 --> 00:39:18,540
Help me!

634
00:39:55,300 --> 00:39:57,300
Didn't I ask you to leave Hua City?

635
00:40:00,540 --> 00:40:01,540
I asked him to come.

636
00:40:03,820 --> 00:40:05,140
I thought he could help.

637
00:40:05,140 --> 00:40:06,020
I called him over.

638
00:40:06,980 --> 00:40:08,700
I really didn't know you asked him to leave.

639
00:40:10,540 --> 00:40:11,500
Come and help.

640
00:40:26,340 --> 00:40:27,180
It's all here.

641
00:40:32,020 --> 00:40:33,020
Take care of the body.

642
00:41:04,020 --> 00:41:05,420
You, come back with me to the police department.

643
00:41:05,740 --> 00:41:06,900
Get in the car and I'll teach you what to say.

644
00:41:07,180 --> 00:41:07,740
Okay.

645
00:41:13,930 --> 00:41:14,770
Officer Liao.

646
00:41:14,900 --> 00:41:16,220
What else can I do for you?

647
00:41:16,450 --> 00:41:17,290
Help?

648
00:41:18,740 --> 00:41:20,700
Do you want to end up like him?

649
00:41:29,780 --> 00:41:31,370
Don't worry. They're the police.

650
00:41:31,500 --> 00:41:32,420
Leave it to them.

651
00:41:53,120 --> 00:41:55,220
[Name: Chen Mo]

652
00:42:19,780 --> 00:42:20,540
I found it out.

653
00:42:21,020 --> 00:42:23,140
The drug addict cop is called Li Chi.

654
00:42:23,860 --> 00:42:24,540
He's dead.

655
00:42:24,820 --> 00:42:26,420
He has a colleague named Xie Yuan.

656
00:42:26,420 --> 00:42:27,340
He's also died.

657
00:42:27,820 --> 00:42:29,260
But I found someone else even more shocking.

658
00:42:29,660 --> 00:42:30,540
Guess who is he?

659
00:42:32,900 --> 00:42:34,700
Liao Yongjia.

660
00:43:47,260 --> 00:43:48,020
How is it?

661
00:43:48,500 --> 00:43:50,220
My tea here is not bad, right?

662
00:43:54,220 --> 00:43:55,020
Chen Mo.

663
00:43:56,500 --> 00:43:57,660
You gave me money?

664
00:43:57,660 --> 00:43:58,890
What's our relationship?

665
00:43:58,890 --> 00:44:00,420
You're insulting me.

666
00:44:01,060 --> 00:44:02,460
Wait here. I'll drive the car over.

667
00:44:02,460 --> 00:44:03,260
Don't go. Wait for me.
